      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Cognee builds a knowledge graph from heterogeneous inputs via a two-step pipeline: add() to stage data and cognify() to process it."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Four search types cover different retrieval needs: CHUNKS (fast vector), INSIGHTS (graph traversal), SUMMARIES (LLM summaries), GRAPH_COMPLETION (grounded answer)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Scope data with dataset_name / datasets=[...] for multi-user or multi-project isolation."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Default backend (LanceDB + NetworkX + SQLite) requires no external services; swap to Neo4j + Qdrant + Postgres for production."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Run cognify() once per batch at session startup, not on every agent turn \u2014 it makes multiple LLM calls and can take tens of seconds."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
